        </p>
        <p>
            <img class="align-center size-full" src="@Url.Content("~/Content/home/images/document/hanghoa/combo_them_danhap.png")" alt="da-nhap-lieu-them-combo"  />
        </p>

        <p>&nbsp</p>
        <p>
            <h5><b>3. Lưu kết quả :</b></h5><br />
        </p>
